---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Workflows — OpenClaw + Claude Code" description="Battle-tested workflows for OpenClaw and Claude Code, from quick fixes to autonomous runs.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-green sm:text-3xl"><span class="text-green">/</span>workflows</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-text-secondary"><span class="text-green">#</span> practical playbooks for shipping faster</p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="/openclaw" class="rounded-lg border border-green/30 bg-green/[0.04] p-4 transition-all hover:border-green">
        <h2 class="font-mono text-base font-semibold text-green">OpenClaw-first workflows</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary">Agent orchestration, channel routing, cron reminders, memory-powered follow-ups.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/claude-code" class="rounded-lg border border-cyan/30 bg-cyan/5 p-4 transition-all hover:border-cyan">
        <h2 class="font-mono text-base font-semibold text-cyan">Claude Code workflows</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary">Quick fixes, feature branches, reviews, and autonomous remote runs.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
      <article class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-green">1) Fast patch (5–10 min)</h3>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded border border-border bg-bg-tertiary p-3 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary">claude -p "fix failing auth tests in src/auth.ts"
claude -p "explain root cause + minimal diff"</pre>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-muted">Use for focused bugfixes with low coordination overhead.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-green">2) OpenClaw dispatch + status updates</h3>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded border border-border bg-bg-tertiary p-3 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary"># spawn ACP session (Codex/Claude/Gemini harness)
sessions_spawn runtime="acp" agentId="codex" thread=true mode="session" \
  task="Implement migration guard + test coverage"

# announce progress in channel
message action=send channel=discord target="#builder" message="Done. Built X, tests green."</pre>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-muted">Use when collaboration or long-running execution is needed.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-green">3) Autonomous 30+ minute run</h3>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded border border-border bg-bg-tertiary p-3 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary">claude --remote "Implement feature X from PRD.
Pause at architecture decisions.
Open PR with test results + rollback plan."</pre>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-muted">Best for mobile handoff + async steering.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-green">4) Daily release watch + reminders</h3>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded border border-border bg-bg-tertiary p-3 font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary"># changelogs.info tracks releases daily
# optional OpenClaw reminder job
cron add schedule="0 9 * * *" payload.kind="systemEvent" \
  payload.text="Reminder: review OpenClaw + Claude Code release notes"</pre>
        <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-text-muted">Use to keep team configs aligned with upstream changes.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
